SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM keyword AS k,
        movie_info AS mi,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE k.keyword = 'marvel-cinematic-universe'
    AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
    AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.title LIKE 'Vampire%'
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id;

SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM keyword AS k,
        movie_info AS mi,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'fight')
    AND mi.info IN ('Bulgaria')
    AND t.production_year > 2000
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id;

        movie_info AS mi,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
    AND mi.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror')
    AND t.production_year > 2005
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id

SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM keyword AS k,
        movie_info AS mi,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE k.keyword = 'marvel-cinematic-universe'
    AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%' AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
    AND t.production_year > 2000
  AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%'
       OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%')
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id;

SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM keyword AS k,
        movie_info AS mi,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE k.keyword LIKE '%sequel%'
    AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%' AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%'
    AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id;
5:
SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM keyword AS k,
        movie_info AS mi,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE k.keyword LIKE '%sequel%'
    AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American')
    AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010
    AND t.id = mi.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id;
